Interface Container<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - keys for the values inside the container, each value should have a unique key
    V - values inside the container
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DatabaseContainer

    public interface Container<K,V>
extends java.lang.Iterable<V>
    Allows the implementing object to act as a container for data allowing for ordered and fast retrieval of data.

    1.0
    Author:
